 "remarks": "Presenting Baypointe! The South End&apos;s community takes luxury a step further! Unique, yet classic and timeless! This oversized 2br 2bth unit industrial-chic w/ fabulous water views- features a spacious floorplan and fabulous water views! - Chef&apos;s well designed kitchen with high end cabinetry, stainless steel appliances- gas stove, dishwasher, microwave, gorgeous quartz countertops, breakfast bar that opens into sunfilled living area w/ dramatic oversized windows, high ceilings, Large master bedroom w/ walk in closet- for ample storage, generous sized 2nd bedroom w/ full bathroom, central air conditioning, full sized washer/dryer, convenient access to waterfront park and harbor boardwalk, Resort style amenities- urban terrace w/ heated salt water pool and lounge areas, fireside lounge w/ kitchen for entertaining, gaming room w/ billiards and shuffleboard, state of the art fitness studio, outdoor living room w/ fireplace and barbecues, complimentary shuttle to Stamford train station, wifi, package reception- Pet friendly! Excellent location just off I-95 along Long Island Sound offers stunning water views-minutes to incredible shopping and restaurants- this is the height of luxury living! Old Greenwich border!",
